UI Flow Test Cases

Total test cases: 14
Framework: Textual + syrupy

Test Cases

  • Check Code Column - Test that the table displays a check code column for transactions
  • File Watcher External Changes - Test file watcher detecting external changes
  • Multi Balance Display Test - Test the multi-balance display system with target, cleared+pending, and delta
  • Multi Balance Display Test - No Snapshot - Test the multi-balance display system without snapshots to check for runtime errors
  • reactive_labels_test - Test that labels update reactively when values change
  • Reconcile All Pending - Test reconciling all pending transactions using 'c' key
  • Reconcile All with Confirmation - Test the confirmation dialog for reconcile all command with both acceptance and cancellation
  • Refresh From File - Test the ability to manually refresh from file using 'r' key
  • Reverse Sort Order - Test the ability to reverse the sort order of transactions
  • simplified_filtering_test - Test that simplified filtering works correctly
  • Table Layout Test - Test table layout with both short and long transaction descriptions
  • Target Balance Adjustment Modal - Test the target balance adjustment modal dialog functionality
  • Toggle Single Posting - Test toggling a single posting from uncleared to pending using spacebar
  • Toggle Transaction Header Status - Test toggling between mixed and uniform posting statuses
